VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT ObjectStateFormatter\.Deserialize\s*\(|LosFormatter\.Deserialize\s*\(|NetDataContractSerializer\s*\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:trusted|allowlist|validate|SerializationBinder && MISSING:test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects additional insecure .NET serialization formatters susceptible to gadget-chain attacks.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Insecure Deserialization: ObjectStateFormatter and LosFormatter.
